<h1 id="about-razortooth">About Razortooth</h1>
<p>This slot is set in a prehistoric forest. It is a colourful prehistoric setting filled with animals from the last ice age. The symbols are primarily animals like mammoth’s, woolly rhinoceros’, bears and of course the Razortooth tigers that give the game its name. There are also gems in the game for some strange reason.<br>
The slot has 243 bet lines and two special features.</p>
<h2 id="game-features">Game Features</h2>
<p>With a grand total of 243 bet lines and a nice set of special features this is a slot that allows for really high maximum win. In fact, the max win has more in common with most jackpot games than with a regular slot. One thing to note is that the bet lines work a bit differently from most slots. Instead you win whenever you get three or more of the same symbol in a straight line.<br>
In any normal game round there is a chance that a Razortooth tiger will leap across the screen leaving three wilds in its wake. On top of that there are free spins where at least one entire wheel is covered in wilds.</p>
<h3 id="the-hunt-random-wild-feature">The Hunt Random Wild Feature</h3>
<p>During any regular game round this feature can get randomly activated. It places three wild symbols in the game. This feature only activates during a regular game round, never during free spins.</p>
<h3 id="savage-wild-free-spins">Savage Wild Free Spins</h3>
<p>When three or more Bonus Scatter symbols show up they activate the Savage Wild Free Spins feature. When this happens five free play rounds where one or two entire wheels are covered in wilds activates. Calculating wins is done just as normal in this mode but it’s worth mentioning that you cannot win more free spins while in this mode. This is because the scatter symbols are never showing up while this feature is active.</p>
